      <a href="/besoins/rides" class="nc2 rv"><div class="ni2"><svg viewBox="0 0 64 64"><g stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 22c0-4 4-8 11-8s11 4 11 8c0 8-1 14-4 19-2 3-4 6-7 7-3-1-5-4-7-7-3-5-4-11-4-19z" fill="currentColor" opacity=".1" stroke-width="1.5" /><path d="M24 20c4-1 12-1 16 0" opacity=".55" stroke-dasharray="3 2" /><path d="M25 24c3-1 11-1 14 0" opacity=".4" stroke-dasharray="3 2" /></g></svg></div><h4>Traiter les rides</h4><p>Front, lion, pattes d'oie</p></a>
